## View Customization

   - Go to Asset app.
     - The customized "New Asset Field" is added in the Asset application.
     - When the value of the field is changed. It will be set OLD on save based on the sample customization logic.

## View Customization

   - Go to Asset app.
     - The customized "New Asset Field" is added in the Asset application.
     - When the value of the field is changed. It will be set OLD on save based on the sample customization logic.


  ![image](images/asset.png)
